videos.description: Joseph Girard III bricks a 3-pointer, but Marek Dolezaj rushes to the hoop for an offensive rebound and layup.
videos.headline: Dolezaj gets putback layup

videos.description: Before Syracuse's game vs. Duke, each team holds an 8 second moment of silence to honor Kobe Bryant. Mike Krzyzewski then describes the importance of Bryant to his family.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Duke, Syracuse hold 8 second moment of silence for Kobe) 2020/02/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Duke, Syracuse hold 8 second moment of silence for Kobe

videos.description: Duke's Alex O'Connell attempts a 3-pointer but Syracuse's Elijah Hughes rises up and swats the ball into the stands.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hughes swats O'Connell's shot into the stands) 2020/02/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hughes swats O'Connell's shot into the stands

videos.description: Vernon Carey Jr. grabs a rebound and immediately throws a deep ball ahead to Cassius Stanley who leaps to catch it, then quickly goes up for a layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Stanley catches Carey's long ball, scores a layup) 2020/02/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stanley catches Carey's long ball, scores a layup
